{"id":149078,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/简讯：北京守望教会信众再次被抓/","date":"2011-05-01T16:30:26Z","modified":"2011-05-01T16:30:26Z","title":"简讯：北京守望教会信众再次被抓","content":"<div>\n<p>总部设在美国的对华援助协会称，北京地下守望教会的信众星期天再次被警察抓捕。</p>\n<p>对华援助协会称，至少31名守望教会的基督徒早上被警察带走，送往不同的警察局或派出所。</p>\n<p>这是连续第四个星期天传出守望教会教友被警方抓捕的消息。</p>\n<p>一周前，守望教会号召在北京中关村举行复活节聚会，至少34名教徒被警察带走。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>\t<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2011/05/#page-top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><br />\n\t\t<span>点击</span><br />\n\t\t<span>页首</span><br />\n\t</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/QbqXD693mwjWc76QeJOHTmAOq3o/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/QbqXD693mwjWc76QeJOHTmAOq3o/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/QbqXD693mwjWc76QeJOHTmAOq3o/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/QbqXD693mwjWc76QeJOHTmAOq3o/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/rsZwVjTAFgQ\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[9729]}